column1: These rates include residential delivery charges, delivery area surcharge (residential and commercial), and fuel surcharge.

For extended residential, a delivery area surcharge of $6.65 per package may apply, and for extended commercial, a delivery area surcharge of $3.05 may apply. For other FedEx fees and shipping information, see the FedEx Service Guide at fedex.com/serviceguide.
We reserve the right to modify, amend, or supplement our rates.
Go to https://www.fedex.com/en-us/service-guide.html for additional rate, fee, and surcharge information.
